 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">购买须知</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 12px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 1px dashed rgb(214, 58, 49); height: 1px; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(214, 58, 49); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　“诚正”艺术平台在保护艺术家艺术作品数字版权的基础上，实现真实可信的数字与实体艺术品的发行、收藏和使用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　1、仅限实名认证为年满18周岁的中国大陆用户购买。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　2、艺术作品的版权由艺术家或艺术机构所有，用户除获得版权方的书面同意以外，不得将艺术作品用于任何商业用途，包括但不限于出售艺术作品的副本、使用权、衍生作品。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　3、“诚正”艺术平台销售的数字形态的艺术作品一经售出，不支持退换。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　4、请勿对艺术作品进行炒作、场外交易、欺诈，或以任何其他非法方式进行使用。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/RGVeicC0CVNX8BCXVRumVUH7lFDZ3Rk7GBWJibLiaRqnJ5UicHwM7pwkNuymzzVL8SAkzfSybFIqbfC9t5BfIBpP5Q/640?wx_fmt=gif\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" data-imgqrcoded=\"1\" data-imgid=\"0.38123935331477976\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; caret-color: red; width: 578px; height: auto !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></section></section>', '2022-07-07 09:59:20', 0, 1);
